{"tid":539225,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陶傑：大學以普通話及格為畢業強制條件，本身就荒謬！","createTime":"2018-01-24T11:12:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-24T13:10:09.000Z","uid":48083,"like":123,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"612c4f1f3b3d745a4e63c962d03a40f6c08921cf","tid":539225,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T11:12:46.000Z","msg":"大學以普通話及格為畢業強制條件，本身就荒謬。澳門的特首普通話宣誓笑死人，為何不予 DQ? 香港大學醫學系畢業，如果科科成績 A，但普通話不合格，是不是不准畢業，令香港少一個醫生？<br />\n<br />\n浸大這個學生會會長抗爭激烈，即使有問題，但校方更傻，講句粗口，即予停學。社會同情，轉向這位學生。<br />\n<br />\n浸會大學是基督教長老所辦，主張博愛包容，咦，而家又唔「包容」嗱？<br />\n<br />\n佢FB"},{"pid":"ab5414722e8d18cf2a4b96b826cc85dc2ace94e8","tid":539225,"uid":11001,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T11:14:00.000Z","msg":"死耶撚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ad35615c289566d01f61fad028075ee513164c3","tid":539225,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T11:16:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f313fa126c756485ec348dea5ed041db809dcea6","tid":539225,"uid":22913,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T11:21:26.000Z","msg":"講左粗口就係十惡不赦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbd44571c4ba51721e59d86c0cd8d1b72f0b6586","tid":539225,"uid":54959,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T11:24:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講左粗口就係十惡不赦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n反港共果啲人就係<br />\n差佬就唔影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"881557951defedf9b29c2ce1d197d725e9b12b8d","tid":539225,"uid":126175,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"cbd44571c4ba51721e59d86c0cd8d1b72f0b6586","tid":539225,"uid":54959,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T11:24:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講左粗口就係十惡不赦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/